Fake profile accounts in the social networking websites.
  One of the problems with Social Networking Webistes being poor user authentication mechanisms. 
  Usually, the accounts are created with the help of an email ids. As the creation of email ids are very easy, lots of fake accounts can be created in the social networking websites that uses poor user authntication. 
  Downside being wastages of resources on the organisation side, and user experience is greatly affected. 
  
  Solutions: 
  1. User authentication by Phone numbers
  2. Using captchas
  3. ???
  
